front.title: •RR'uruurrr
front.gametext: Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 while armed with a Gaderffi Stick. Where present, each of your banthas is power and forfeit +2 unless a Weequay is at a related site. When 'riding' a bantha, adds one battle destiny.
front.lore: Tusken Raider who tends to the banthas used by URoRRuR'R'R's tribe. Expert in wielding a gaffi stick. Attacked Luke Skywalker in the Jundland Wastes.
